Locals often joke that if you randomly throw a stone, you are likely to hit a professor’s head.A rough count of current and deceased professors in the area seems to give credence to the  legend. While Gem may not be a popular tourist destination, the Sub County tucked in Siaya County boasts of distinguished professors and scholars, not only in the country but also in the region.
So widespread are the academicians that locals often joke that if you randomly throw a stone, you are likely to hit a professor’s head.



